      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. Mechanically, the engine starts reliably and the transmission shifts through all gears, though it lacks the crispness of a newer model. There are visible cosmetic flaws, including some paint fading on the hood and minor scuffs along the bumpers, as well as some wear on the interior upholstery. It is a solid, functional car that has been used regularly, making it ideal for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
