    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute mint condition. This vehicle serves as a benchmark for the model, featuring a flawless exterior profile and a cabin that remains in showroom-state. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, it has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets the standards of the most exacting collector. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
