      "description": "Hey everyone! Check out this absolute beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car that it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in flawless condition and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come see it for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
